      • toCommandString

        public abstract java.lang.String toCommandString()
        Returns a String in a very specific format. The String must match the protocol for this command, such that every String matches the pattern of the example. Also must the static method toCommand return a copy of this command, using the returned String.
        Returns:
        A command string that represents this Command
